BobUI 5.0.2 is a bug-fix release. It maintains both forward and backward
compatibility (source and binary) with BobUI 5.0.0 and 5.0.1.

For more details, refer to the online documentation included in this
distribution. The documentation is also available online:

  http://bobui-project.org/doc/bobui-5.0/

Some of the changes listed in this file include issue tracking numbers
corresponding to tasks in the BobUI Bug Tracker:

  http://bugreports.bobui-project.org/

Each of these identifiers can be entered in the bug tracker to obtain more
information about a particular change.


****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

General Improvements
--------------------

 - Lots of fixes to enable static builds on Windows, Linux and Mac.

****************************************************************************
*                          Library                                         *
****************************************************************************

BobUICore
-----

 - [BOBUIBUG-29130] Fixed compilation when connecting with the new syntax to a
   signal that has more than 3 registered meta type arguments, and the compiler
   does not support variadic templates

BobUIGui
-----

 - [BOBUIBUG-14766] Fixed potential access violation in QPixmap::copy() for <32 bit pixmaps.
 - [BOBUIBUG-24762] Fixed dashes being rendered differently depending on system clip.
 - [BOBUIBUG-25036] Fixed artifacts when drawing same line with different clips.
 - [BOBUIBUG-29643] Fixed crashes when using QImage in combination with QCoreApplication.

BobUIWidgets
---------

 - [BOBUIBUG-28817] Fixed QColorDialog::setOption(), QFontDialog::setOption().
 - [BOBUIBUG-29680] Fix mouse double click events not bubbling up to parent widgets.

BobUINetwork
---------

 - [BOBUIBUG-29103] Toggle on demand loading of root certs properly.

BobUIConcurrent
------------

 - [BOBUIBUG-28984] Fix compilation of BobUI Concurrent with gcc 4.3.

BobUISql
-----

 - Fix QSqlTableModel:revert() for OnFieldChange.
 - [BOBUIBUG-29102] Support refreshing inserted rows with auto columns.
 - [BOBUIBUG-29108] Fix QSqlTableModel::headerData() for empty query with inserted row.
 - [BOBUIBUG-29217] Fix QSqlTableModel::setData() for non-change detection.

