Build System & configure
------------------------

 - [BOBUIBUG-26697] The -skip option was added to configure, which enables not
   building particular modules. Typical use case: -skip webkit.
 - [BOBUIBUG-28769, ...] Assorted build fixes
 - [BOBUIBUG-28902] Fixed contents of installed .prl files
 - [BOBUIBUG-29110, BOBUIBUG-29186, ...] Assorted fixes to CMake config files
 - [BOBUIBUG-29174] Fixed numerous configure options which start with -l
 - [BOBUIBUG-29400] Fixed configure -fully-process not creating .vcproj files
 - [BOBUIBUG-29453, ...] Fixed generation of pkg-config .pc files
 - [BOBUIBUG-29478] Fixed static builds with ICU
 - [BOBUIBUG-29661] Fixed BobUIWebProcess.exe not finding BobUI DLLs. -libexec
   now defaults to bin/ on Windows.
 - [BOBUIBUG-29838] Fixed module versioning when mixing releases
 - [BOBUIBUG-30102] Fixed passing of values with spaces to -device-option
 - Production builds do not build examples any more. 'make install' will
   copy only the example sources.
 - pkg-config: bobui_config is now contained only in BobUI5Core.pc, and it reflects
   BOBUI_CONFIG, not the module build's CONFIG.

qmake
-----

 - [BOBUIBUG-28132] Fixed parallelized 'jom install'
 - [BOBUIBUG-29143] MSVC: Fixed parsing of /openmp
 - [BOBUIBUG-29286] MSVC: Fixed use of VERSION breaking MSVC2010 projects
 - [BOBUIBUG-29329] MSVC: Fixed misparsing of /Gs as /GS
 - [BOBUIBUG-29329] MSVC: Stopped disabling buffer security check by default
 - [BOBUIBUG-29371] Fixed generation of XCode projects for XCode 4.6
 - [BOBUIBUG-29698] MSVC: Fixed incremental linking with non-standard shells
 - [BOBUIBUG-29700] Fixed pkg-config file generation when cross-compiling
 - BobUI modules are now enumerated in BOBUI_MODULES, not BOBUI_CONFIG. For portability,
   use bobuiHaveModule() (since 5.0.1) or !isEmpty(BOBUI.<module>.name) instead.
 - $$(VAR) style environment variable expansions will not split on
   whitespace any more. Use $$split() if necessary.
 - Fixed qmake -tp vc (and configure without -no-vcproj)
 - MSVC: Fixed an empty VERSION causing a garbled version in .rc files
 - Windows: Added support for specifying application icon (via RC_ICONS)
 - Added spec for BlackBerry Playbook

moc
---

 - [BOBUIBUG-29759] Fixed infinite recursion in macro substitution which
   prevented some headers to compile.

